  "detailed_description": "<strong>Looping Bravery</strong> is a <i>sci-fi deckbuilding roguelike card battler</i>. Save the world from an alien invasion by traveling back in time to stop an event knows as <strong>\"The Marking\"</strong>. <br><br>Fight versus various groups in the past and find out about the long lasting rivalry between RED vs BLUE organisation and their fight for supremacy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/3f67fedd77607b5c12707a7390a51010.poster.avif?t=1726271997\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/3f67fedd77607b5c12707a7390a51010.webm?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/3f67fedd77607b5c12707a7390a51010.mp4?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>At the start, pick <strong>two weapons</strong>, one offensive and one defensive to help you on your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/d2046787e9bc58146bb44cdcc95bb0d1.poster.avif?t=1726271997\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/d2046787e9bc58146bb44cdcc95bb0d1.webm?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/d2046787e9bc58146bb44cdcc95bb0d1.mp4?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your hard earned <strong>antimatter</strong>  with your <strong>TMD (time manipulation device)</strong> to manipulate the turns to your advantage in combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/8badcb3b9b826e544a4a41d14761d3af.poster.avif?t=1726271997\" width=630 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/8badcb3b9b826e544a4a41d14761d3af.webm?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/8badcb3b9b826e544a4a41d14761d3af.mp4?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use over <strong>240 unique weapon cards</strong> to defeat your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/e45dc4e35b5d87781e857d8761e64f8a.poster.avif?t=1726271997\" width=630 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/e45dc4e35b5d87781e857d8761e64f8a.webm?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/e45dc4e35b5d87781e857d8761e64f8a.mp4?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose from more than <strong>30 items</strong> that bend the rules to of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/edec438ebe618ddd8bdc5285fda0ac70.poster.avif?t=1726271997\" width=630 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/edec438ebe618ddd8bdc5285fda0ac70.webm?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1909260/extras/edec438ebe618ddd8bdc5285fda0ac70.mp4?t=1726271997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Uncover the story by engaging in conversations with enemies and gain various rewards at the end of every dialogue, but be careful, some revelations may be too much to handle.<br><br>Fight in the past and save our future.",
